feat: hash-based URL routing — refresh tetap di halaman yang sama

- handleNavigate sekarang set window.location.hash
- useEffect di mount restore currentPage dari hash URL
- popstate listener handle back/forward browser
- Semua halaman punya URL: /#beranda, /#profil, /#ppdb, /#dashboard, dll
- Zero dependencies, cuma 1 file diubah (App.tsx)

